\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16262158 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13324050\charrsid8147471 Is that quite a big thing in town?
