\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6381548 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13324050\charrsid8147471 No, I don't think so. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16262158 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13324050\charrsid8147471 So she was fairly easy going?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6381548 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13324050\charrsid8147471 Yes, she was - like that.
