\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16262158 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13324050\charrsid8147471 Your father had a bicycle didn't he? Was he telling me about seeing the first bicycle?
