\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6381548 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13324050\charrsid8147471 Yes, and help with a neighbour.
